lines.text: i beat my machine it's a part of me
it's inside of me
i'm stuck in this dream it's changing me
i am becoming
the me that you know-
had some second thoughts
he's covered with scabs
and he is broken and sore
the me that you know-
doesn't come around much
that part of me isn't here anymore
all pain disappears it's the nature-
of my circuitry
drowns out all i hear no escape from this-
my new consciousness-
that me that you know
used- to have feelings
but the blood has stopped pumping
and he's left to decay
the me that you know
is now made up of wires
and even when i'm right with you
i'm so far away-
i can try to get away
but i've strapped myself in
i can try to scratch away
the sound in my ears-
i can see it killing away
all my bad parts-
i don't want to listen-
but it's all too clear
hiding backwards inside of me
i feel so unafraid
annie, hold a little tighter
i might just slip away
it won't give up it wants me dead
